Package se.kth.iv1350.retailStore.dto

Class SaleDTO

java.lang.Object
se.kth.iv1350.retailStore.dto.SaleDTO
public class SaleDTO extends Object
This class represents the data transfer object (DTO) for a sale. It contains all relevant information about a sale, including sale ID, items involved in the sale, total price, VAT, discount, and payment details.

    • SaleDTO

      public SaleDTO(String saleId, ItemRegister itemRegister, Period salePeriod, Payment payment)
      Creates a SaleDTO object that holds all relevant information about a sale.
      Parameters:
      saleId - Unique ID for this sale.
      itemRegister - Contains the list of all sold items.
      salePeriod - Includes the time when the sale started and ended.
      payment - Contains calculated price and VAT information.

    • SaleDTO

      public SaleDTO(SaleDTO saleDTO, Payment payment)
      Creates a new SaleDTO that includes payment details like amount paid and change.
      Parameters:
      saleDTO - The existing sale data without payment info.
      payment - The payment that was made by the customer.
